Manuscript Master App
A Python-based GUI application for the enhancement and binarization of historical manuscripts.

Technical Overview
This tool uses advanced image processing pipelines to clean scanned documents, including:

Noise Reduction: Gaussian, Median, and Non-Local Means filtering.

Enhancement: Contrast Limited Adaptive Histogram Equalization (CLAHE).

Binarization: Hybrid Sauvola-Otsu and Adaptive Gaussian thresholding.

Validation: Canny Edge detection masking for stroke preservation.

